Stephen King novel comes out,

00:02:45.350 --> 00:02:47.386
he sucks all the
air out of the room.

00:02:47.386 --> 00:02:48.632
[LAUGHTER]

00:02:48.632 --> 00:02:51.215
MALE SPEAKER: So there's like,
